  {
    "hotel_id": "2090169",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/toyoko-inn-cebu/hotel/cebu-ph.html",
    "name": "Toyoko INN Cebu",
    "detail": "Excellent accommodations. Great water park for the children. Free Asian style breakfast. Only coffee, tea, hard boiled or scrambled eggs, toast, butter and jam for the Westerners. Very good quality. The rooms are comfortable. The Air Conditioning works very well. The TV has limited channels and like all other hotels in Cebu very little to watch but Asian shows and movies. Only 2 stations with western movies. The best part is the hot water! A constant flow of water soooo hot one must temper it with some cold to take a bath or shower. This is unheard of in Asia except for over priced hotels. Reminds me to mention, the prices are very affordable. Joining the Toyoko Club reduces them even further and offers numerous other advantages. Toyoko is adjacent to a very nice small JMall. Everything is available but in a well conceived layout instead of the confusing mazes of the larger malls in Cebu. The grocery story is excellent! Tons of international products. We'll stay here every visit!",
